“\n”,
“Now we calculate the **Morality of the System** M(S) for each narrative pattern.\n”,
“\n”,
“### M(S) = (R_e × A × D × C) - L\n”,
“\n”,
“Where:\n”,
“- **R_e** (Resonance): Coupling strength between components\n”,
“- **A** (Adaptability): Response capacity to change\n”,
“- **D** (Diversity): Pathway multiplicity\n”,
“- **C** (Curiosity): Exploration rate\n”,
“- **L** (Loss): Waste, suppression, inefficiency\n”,
“\n”,
“### Translating Cultural Patterns to Geometric Variables”
]
},
