“                        pattern_characteristics: Dict = None) -> Dict:\n”,
“        """\n”,
“        Assess if a narrative shows high geometric coherence\n”,
“        \n”,
“        In production, this would analyze actual text.\n”,
“        For this demo, we use pre-computed characteristics.\n”,
“        """\n”,
“        \n”,
“        # In real implementation, extract these from narrative_text\n”,
“        # For now, use provided characteristics\n”,
